title: [Cadie's Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath a stained mahogany ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the smooth sandstone walls.  A floral-etched ceramic case and a small brown box sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on a patterned hardwood floor.

Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A floral-etched ceramic case and a small brown box sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.
